OL,3,CPolice threaten 'action' over online
OL,4,Cspeculation in schoolboy murder case
OL,6,FPolice are warning the public they
OL,7,Fwill "take action" against anyone who
OL,8,Fjeopardises the investigation into the
OL,9,Fmurder of a boy at a school in
OL,10,FSheffield.
OL,12,FFifteen-year-old Harvey Willgoose died
OL,13,Fafter being stabbed at All Saints
OL,14,FCatholic High School on Monday.
OL,16,FA 15-year-old boy was arrested at the
OL,17,Fscene and remains in custody.
