OL,3,CPolice threaten 'action' over online
OL,4,Cspeculation in schoolboy murder case
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police have cautioned
OL,7,Fpeople against speculating about the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of the incident amid
OL,9,Fconcern that the suspect was being
OL,10,Fnamed online.
OL,12,FAssistant Chief Constable Lindsey
OL,13,FButterfield said: "Our investigation
OL,14,Finto Harvey's death is continuing at
OL,15,Fpace and with this in mind, I would
OL,16,Furge people to avoid unhelpful online
OL,17,Fspeculation and identifying anyone who
OL,18,Fthey believe to be involved in this
OL,19,Ftragic incident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
