OL,6,F"Identifying a suspect can prejudice
OL,7,Fcourt proceedings and risks justice
OL,8,Fnot being secured for Harvey and his
OL,9,Ffamily.
OL,11,F"We will take action against those who
OL,12,Fpose a risk to judicial proceedings
OL,13,Fand I want to remind people of their
OL,14,Fresponsibility around what they share
OL,15,Fand post online and the potential
OL,16,Fimpact it can have on justice."
OL,18,FThe force later disabled comments on
OL,19,Fits own Facebook post about the
OL,20,Fwarning after it sparked speculation
OL,21,Fabout the case.
