OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We are aware
OL,7,Fthat some comments on this post are
OL,8,Fcontinuing harmful speculation which
OL,9,Fcould be detrimental to our
OL,10,Finvestigation. To protect the
OL,11,Fintegrity of our investigation, we are
OL,12,Fdisabling comments on the post."
