OL,6,FIf a child is charged with an offence
OL,7,Fand is facing criminal proceedings in
OL,8,Fadult courts ` magistrates' and crown
OL,9,Fcourts ` then magistrates and judges
OL,10,Fcan grant them anonymity, along with
OL,11,Fwitnesses and victims.
OL,13,FThe law bans the press from publishing
OL,14,Fa child defendant's name or any detail
OL,15,Fwhich could lead to them being
OL,16,Fidentified while the reporting
OL,17,Frestrictions are in place.
