OL,6,FThe automatic restrictions technically
OL,7,Fbegin once court proceedings are
OL,8,Factive ` when a suspect has been
OL,9,Fcharged and is appearing in court for
OL,10,Fthe first time.
OL,12,FBut media organisations typically
OL,13,Frefrain from identifying any child
OL,14,Farrested on suspicion of a crime,
OL,15,Fhaving considered their ethical and
OL,16,Fother legal responsibilities.
