OL,6,FThere are exceptions. Before his
OL,7,Ftrial, the media was allowed to
OL,8,Fidentify the Southport killer Axel
OL,9,FRudakubana as he was days away from
OL,10,Fturning 18.
OL,12,FJudge Andrew Menary KC said at the
OL,13,Ftime: "Continuing to prevent the full
OL,14,Freporting has the disadvantage of
OL,15,Fallowing others to spread
OL,16,Fmisinformation, in a vacuum."
OL,18,FDespite a huge emergency services
OL,19,Fresponse, Harvey died after an
OL,20,Fincident at 12.17pm on Monday.
