OL,6,FThe attack happened five days after
OL,7,Flockdown measures were implemented at
OL,8,Fthe school following another incident.
OL,10,FA message to parents at the time said
OL,11,Fthere had been "threats of violence"
OL,12,Fbetween a "small number of students".
OL,14,FFollowing news of Harvey's death
OL,15,Fformer children's commissioner Anne
OL,16,FLongfield said schools should not be
OL,17,Fturned into "fortresses" in response
OL,18,Fto knife crime involving teenagers.
OL,20,FShe said the issue was "national
OL,21,Fcrisis that needs a national response".
